  "_note": "The live database connection AND all Auth0 settings (user JWT validation on this 'api' audience, plus the M2M client used to call the Scheduler -- see common::auth0) are read at runtime from ~/.@(Model.Name).json by the common Config loader -- add an 'auth0' section there (domain, audiences.api, m2m_clients.scheduler), not here. This file plays no part in Auth0 configuration; it exists only for parity with the .NET appsettings.json layout. The API binds to the first free port in 5200-5300."
